@TemasekFoundation is doing a second round of reusable mask distribution after the positive response to the first round. Reusable masks are a good option as they protect us against viruses and ease the strain on our environment.

From today to 4 Oct, Singapore residents holding a government issued ID can collect two free reusable masks each from vending machines located at CCs, RCs and bus interchanges. Child-size masks are available at certain locations. More details on mask collection and pre-orders can be found at https://mask.stayprepared.sg&nbsp;

For my Teck Ghee residents, you can collect your free adult and child-size masks at Teck Ghee CC. Adult masks are also available at RCs and RNs. You can check the above website for availability. ‚Äì LHL
